  "description": "With up to 75 lumens, this little light will help keep you seen, day or night. The KTV Pro uses 2 powerful red LEDs and a custom engineered reflector to provides over 270\u00b0 of visibility. Five different modes have you covered, from a low steady on, all the way to a powerful daytime flash. Easy USB-charging comes via an integrated plug, simply pop off the rear cover and plug your light right into any standard USB port and you\u2019re charging, no cable needed. The tool free mount fits round seat posts or aero posts, letting you swap the light between your trusty commuter and your race-bred steed.5 lighting modes, 2 in steady and 3 in flashing; steady: 20 lumens (4h), 3 lumens (18h), flash 1\u201325 lumens (8.75h), flash 2\u201310 lumens (19.5h) and day flash\u201375 lumens (10h).Easy 1-button interface takes you through all your light\u2019s modes.Wide-angle lens that provides over 270\u00b0 of visibility.Aero post compatible mount.Integrated USB plug means you don\u2019t need to carry a charging cable \u2013 full charging takes ~3 hours.LED charging indicator lets you know light needs charging, when it\u2019s charging and when it\u2019s ready to go.Silicone, tool-free mounting straps.IPX7 waterproofing protects your light from heavy downpours.",
